of Lomax's itinerary and dates.

00:10:50.380 --> 00:10:54.840 position:56%
The state has prepared the materials
for analysis and comparison.

00:10:54.840 --> 00:10:58.830 position:56%
It is now possible to identify
concordances between this collection

00:10:58.830 --> 00:11:00.690
and the one in Barcelona.

00:11:00.690 --> 00:11:04.040
Mutual enrichment between
collection can first be achieved

00:11:04.040 --> 00:11:05.720
