of mid-20th century Spain.

00:11:20.400 --> 00:11:24.190
At the same time, through
the social networks

00:11:24.190 --> 00:11:27.420
to which the database is
connected, Lomax's contribution

00:11:27.420 --> 00:11:30.500
to Spanish traditional
music can be better known

00:11:30.500 --> 00:11:32.980
and appreciated by
a general audience.

00:11:32.980 --> 00:11:37.960
In order to provide a different
