pro-American narrative.

00:51:33.730 --> 00:51:37.850
However, the right whites
unanimously accused their

00:51:37.850 --> 00:51:40.990
[inaudible] of provoking
and escalating the Civil War

00:51:40.990 --> 00:51:46.290
to win Russia this
[inaudible] people.

00:51:46.290 --> 00:51:48.970
Basically, the white
narrative asserted

00:51:48.970 --> 00:51:51.940
that not only the United States,

00:51:51.940 --> 00:51:56.090
but entire Entente have provoked
the Civil War to force Russia

00:51:56.090 --> 00:52:01.310
