abandoned them to suffer torture

00:52:08.930 --> 00:52:13.400
and death at the hands of
the victorious Red Army.

00:52:13.400 --> 00:52:16.710
According to this narrative,
General William Greaves,

00:52:16.710 --> 00:52:20.710
