allies but to the Bolsheviks.

00:52:29.030 --> 00:52:34.970
And the [inaudible] had generally
financed antigovernment terrorist

00:52:34.970 --> 00:52:37.730
organizations, including
the Bolsheviks,

00:52:37.730 --> 00:52:40.400
to destroy the Russian empire.

00:52:40.400 --> 00:52:45.660
This narrative often noted in
all kind of conspiracy theories

00:52:45.660 --> 00:52:50.030 position:56%
and knowledge [inaudible]
themselves constitute a fertile soil

00:52:50.030 --> 00:52:54.420
