from west to east.

01:04:02.160 --> 01:04:06.160
But because these various Caribbean
populations have been defined

01:04:06.160 --> 01:04:09.580
since their inception as sort of --

01:04:09.580 --> 01:04:12.710
in relation to the European
metropole, they are marginal

01:04:12.710 --> 01:04:17.430
