01:04:17.430 --> 01:04:20.040
in a larger Euro Atlantic context.

01:04:20.040 --> 01:04:22.120
So in essence, my book
is challenging the notion

01:04:22.120 --> 01:04:25.870
of the Caribbean regional and
the Euro Atlantic and arguing

01:04:25.870 --> 01:04:28.840
